lead_paragraph: Zach Randolph scored 25 points and Lance Stephenson added 16 off the bench to lead the Memphis Grizzlies to a 94-88 victory Friday over the Utah Jazz at FedExForum.

headline.print_headline: Randolph Leads Grizzlies to Victory Over Jazz
